The paper deals with the problem of top-n recommendations, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed method involves tensor factorization, which is a popular technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data science (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the modification of standard metrics, which is related to the field of social informatics (cs.SI).
